# Stack
- Python: `uv` (not pip). Use `uv init`, `uv add`, `uv run`
- TypeScript: `bun` (not npm). Use `bun init`, `bun add`, `bun run`

# Style
- Type hints (Python), strict mode (TS)
- Ruff formatting (Python), Prettier (TS/JS)

# Workflow
- Read before edit
- Test before done
